{"type":"message","id":"c547a1ea","parentId":"bab35175","timestamp":"2026-03-21T12:59:18.972Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我明白了！代码中显示 sentiment_report 实际上是在 social_media_analyst 中生成的，而不是单独的 sentiment_analyst。而 game_theory_report 是由 Game Theory Manager 生成的，而不是 game_theory_analyst。\n\n让我更仔细地看一下 social_media_analyst 的实现，确认 sentiment_report 是由它生成的：从之前看到的代码中，social_media_analyst 返回了 \"sentiment_report\"。这意味着当前的架构是：\n- social_media_analyst 负责情绪分析 (sentiment_report)\n- game_theory_manager 负责博弈论分析 (game_theory_report)\n\n但是从报告来看，有专门的\"情绪分析师报告\"和\"博弈论分析师报告\"部分。这意味着实际上需要将这两个功能从现有的分析师中分离出来，创建独立的分析师。\n\n让我检查一下当前使用的 Docker 镜像版本和配置，以便了解需要修改什么：","thinkingSignature":"0fa211b9a090eb90669b6c3f73e97b97a6a55fa252c04e7d94120a01ee528673"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2to1hfwckthb_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace-finance\\TradingAgents-AShare-local\\Dockerfile"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":23884,"output":217,"cacheRead":32468,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56569,"cost":{"input":0.0071652,"output":0.0002604,"cacheRead":0.0009740399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00839964}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774097953849}}
{"type":"message","id":"0f6a2da2","parentId":"c547a1ea","timestamp":"2026-03-21T12:59:18.979Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_2to1hfwckthb_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Stage 1: Build Frontend (始终在原生架构运行以提速)\r\nFROM --platform=$BUILDPLATFORM node:25-slim AS frontend-builder\r\nWORKDIR /app/frontend\r\nCOPY frontend/package*.json ./\r\n# 开启缓存挂载，加速 npm 安装\r\nRUN --mount=type=cache,target=/root/.npm npm install\r\nCOPY frontend/ ./\r\nRUN npm run build\r\n\r\n# Stage 2: Final Image (多架构目标镜像)\r\nFROM ghcr.io/astral-sh/uv:python3.10-bookworm-slim AS runtime\r\nWORKDIR /app\r\n\r\n# 安装基础系统依赖\r\nRUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \\\r\n    curl \\\r\n    && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*\r\n\r\n# 利用 uv 同步依赖（uv 在多架构环境下依然非常快）\r\nCOPY pyproject.toml uv.lock ./\r\nRUN --mount=type=cache,target=/root/.cache/uv \\\r\n    uv sync --frozen --no-install-project --no-dev\r\n\r\n# 拷贝后端源码\r\nCOPY api/ ./api/\r\nCOPY tradingagents/ ./tradingagents/\r\n\r\n# 拷贝在 Stage 1 中快速构建好的前端产物\r\nCOPY --from=frontend-builder /app/frontend/dist ./frontend/dist\r\n\r\n# 暴露端口\r\nEXPOSE 8000\r\n\r\n# 环境变量设置\r\nENV PYTHONUNBUFFERED=1\r\nENV PYTHONPATH=/app\r\n\r\n# 启动命令\r\nCMD [\"uv\", \"run\", \"python\", \"-m\", \"uvicorn\", \"api.main:app\", \"--host\", \"0.0.0.0\", \"--port\", \"8000\"]\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774097958976}}
{"type":"message","id":"59fb3fb6","parentId":"0f6a2da2","timestamp":"2026-03-21T12:59:23.412Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我了解了整个架构。我需要：1. 创建 sentiment_analyst.py - 将情绪分析从 social_media_analyst 中分离出来\n2. 创建 game_theory_analyst.py - 将博弈论分析从 game_theory_manager 中分离出来3. 更新 setup.py 添加这两个新分析师4. 更新 agents/__init__.py 导出新分析师\n\n不过，让我再仔细查看一下现有的 social_media_analyst 和 game_theory_manager，确认它们是否已经做了这部分工作：","thinkingSignature":"d27265d7e9e8feb2b65a5839f420bb6bb7870341d7cfc9644b2dde399dc107c2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_juah9hyicu2y_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace-finance\\TradingAgents-AShare-local\\tradingagents\\agents\\managers\\game_theory_manager.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":24469,"output":158,"cacheRead":32468,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57095,"cost":{"input":0.0073406999999999995,"output":0.0001896,"cacheRead":0.0009740399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.008504339999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774097958980}}
{"type":"message","id":"06c00e3f","parentId":"59fb3fb6","timestamp":"2026-03-21T12:59:23.419Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_juah9hyicu2y_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"from langchain_core.messages import HumanMessage\r\n\r\nfrom tradingagents.dataflows.config import get_config\r\nfrom tradingagents.prompts import get_prompt\r\nfrom tradingagents.agents.utils.debate_utils import extract_tagged_json, strip_tagged_json\r\n\r\n\r\ndef create_game_theory_manager(llm):\r\n    def game_theory_manager_node(state):\r\n        smart_money_report = state.get(\"smart_money_report\", \"无主力资金数据\")\r\n        sentiment_report = state.get(\"sentiment_report\", \"无情绪数据\")\r\n        print(f\"[Game Theory Manager] START smart_money={'有' if smart_money_report != '无主力资金数据' else '无'}, sentiment={'有' if sentiment_report != '无情绪数据' else '无'}\")\r\n        config = get_config()\r\n\r\n        prompt_template = get_prompt(\"game_theory_manager_prompt\", config=config)\r\n        if not prompt_template:\r\n            print(\"[Game Theory Manager] ERROR: Prompt template not found\")\r\n            return {\"game_theory_report\": \"博弈分析提示词模板缺失，无法生成报告。\"}\r\n\r\n        prompt = prompt_template.format(\r\n            smart_money_report=smart_money_report,\r\n            sentiment_report=sentiment_report,\r\n        )\r\n\r\n        result = llm.invoke(prompt)\r\n        structured_signals = extract_tagged_json(result.content, \"GAME_THEORY\")\r\n        cleaned_report = strip_tagged_json(result.content, \"GAME_THEORY\")\r\n        print(f\"[Game Theory Manager] DONE, report length={len(result.content)}\")\r\n        return {\r\n            \"game_theory_report\": cleaned_report,\r\n            \"game_theory_signals\": structured_signals,\r\n        }\r\n\r\n    return game_theory_manager_node\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774097963416}}
