{"type":"message","id":"d97a4458","parentId":"efd45bed","timestamp":"2026-03-21T12:59:32.490Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我查看请求模型的定义：","thinkingSignature":"08d796e652056e9e50dc148cae04e0b888a2ff13e84d80b5a58aa16ef4bc2b0f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d8vhujcwvviw_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace-finance\\TradingAgents-AShare-local\\api\\main.py","offset":290,"limit":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":25494,"output":74,"cacheRead":32468,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58036,"cost":{"input":0.0076482,"output":0.00008879999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0009740399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00871104}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774097970294}}
{"type":"message","id":"6161c0c6","parentId":"d97a4458","timestamp":"2026-03-21T12:59:32.497Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_d8vhujcwvviw_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\nclass AnalyzeRequest(UserContextInput):\r\n    symbol: str = Field(default=\"\", description=\"股票代码，如 600519.SH（当 query 包含代码时可省略）\")\r\n    trade_date: str = Field(default_factory=cn_today_str, description=\"交易日期 YYYY-MM-DD\")\r\n    selected_analysts: List[str] = Field(\r\n        default_factory=lambda: [\"market\", \"social\", \"news\", \"fundamentals\", \"macro\", \"smart_money\"]\r\n    )\r\n    config_overrides: Dict[str, Any] = Field(default_factory=dict)\r\n    dry_run: bool = False\r\n    # When set, triggers intent-driven analysis via streaming dual-horizon path\r\n    query: Optional[str] = Field(default=None, description=\"自然语言查询，如：分析贵州茅台短线机会\")\r\n    horizons: List[str] = Field(default_factory=lambda: [\"short\"], description=\"分析周期列表，如 ['short'] 或 ['short','medium']\")\r\n    # Pre-parsed intent from _ai_extract_symbol_and_date (avoids second LLM call in _run_job)\r\n    user_intent: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = Field(default=None, description=\"预解析的用户意图，由 chat_completions 传入\")\r\n\r\n\r\nclass AnalyzeResponse(BaseModel):\r\n    job_id: str\r\n    status: Literal[\"pending\", \"running\", \"completed\", \"failed\"]\r\n    created_at: str\r\n\r\n\r\nclass JobStatusResponse(BaseModel):\r\n    job_id: str\r\n    status: Literal[\"pending\", \"running\", \"completed\", \"failed\"]\r\n    created_at: str\r\n    started_at: Optional[str] = None\r\n    finished_at: Optional[str] = None\r\n    symbol: str\r\n    trade_date: str\r\n    error: Optional[str] = None\r\n\r\n\r\nclass ChatMessage(BaseModel):\r\n    role: str\r\n    content: Any\r\n\r\n\r\nclass ChatCompletionRequest(UserContextInput):\r\n    model: Optional[str] = \"tradingagents-ashare\"\r\n    messages: List[ChatMessage]\r\n    stream: bool = True\r\n    selected_analysts: List[str] = Field(\r\n        default_factory=lambda: [\"market\", \"social\", \"news\", \"fundamentals\", \"macro\", \"smart_money\"]\r\n    )\r\n    config_overrides: Dict[str, Any] = Field(default_factory=dict)\r\n    dry_run: bool = False\r\n\r\n\r\nclass KlineResponse(BaseModel):\r\n    symbol: str\r\n    start_date: str\r\n    end_date: str\r\n    candles: List[Dict[str, Any]]\r\n\r\n\r\n# Report API Models\r\nclass ReportCreateRequest(BaseModel):\r\n    symbol: str = Field(..., description=\"股票代码\")\r\n    trade_date: str = Field(..., description=\"交易日期 YYYY-MM-DD\")\r\n\n[2487 more lines in file. Use offset=350 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774097972494}}
{"type":"message","id":"fa1c24b3","parentId":"6161c0c6","timestamp":"2026-03-21T12:59:38.493Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！现在我明白了。当前的默认分析师列表是：```python\n[\"market\", \"social\", \"news\", \"fundamentals\", \"macro\", \"smart_money\"]\n```\n\n这就是 6 位分析师。根据报告的输出，实际上需要添加：- \"sentiment\" - 情绪分析师- \"game_theory\" - 博弈论分析师\n\n但是从代码中看到，sentiment_report 实际上是从 social 生成的，game_theory_report 是从 game_theory_manager 生成的。\n\n让我重新检查一下报告，看看这 6 个分析师是如何映射到报告中的 6 个部分的。从报告来看：\n1. 市场分析师 → market\n2. 情绪分析师 → ? (可能是 social)\n3. 新闻分析师 → news\n4. 基本面分析师 → fundamentals\n5. 主力资金分析师 → smart_money6. 博弈论分析师 → game_theory_manager\n\n这意味着 social_media_analyst 实际上同时负责\"社交媒体\"和\"情绪\"分析。而\"博弈论\"是由 Game Theory Manager 负责的。\n\n但是从任务要求来看，用户想要 15 位分析师。让我检查一下在线版 510168 的结构，看看它是如何配置的。\n\n不过首先，让我确认一下当前系统中是否真的只有 6 位分析师。让我查看当前 Docker 容器的运行状态：","thinkingSignature":"357735c2acac862fce3fc6e1881056adb1fe283cc63046da1271f347fd670cb5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ke81s9yshk51_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"docker ps"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":26177,"output":289,"cacheRead":32468,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58934,"cost":{"input":0.0078531,"output":0.00034679999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0009740399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00917394}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774097972498}}
